          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(center)">
                                        <placeName>New York</placeName>
                                        <date>April 17<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1849</date>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(4)"><persName>Dr. Solomon's</persName><lb/> called on
                                        me in answer to my letter in relation<lb/> to your debt. He
                                        says that he is pressed at<lb/> present but will pay in
                                        time, and desires<lb/> me before proceeding to communicate
                                        to you.<lb/> I asked him for part of this claim and<lb/> I
                                        would give him time for the balance<lb/> this he appears not
                                        willing to do. I there<lb/>fore await your answer.</p>
                              <p>From what I know of the<lb/> Doctor's disposition to pay up
                                        (entre<lb/> vous) should advise you to in=<lb/>struct me to
                                        sue him.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(4)">Yours truly</p>
                              <p rend="indent(4)">
                                        <persName role="author">H Morrison</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(4)">
                                        <placeName>No. 6 City Hall place</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">I know <persName>Morrison</persName> is right<lb/>
                                        you'd not obtain a cent <add>?</add> the scoundrel<lb/>
                                        <add>?</add>, and if you wish to obtain your<lb/> money it
                                        will have be done, why should<lb/> he go to <placeName><hi
                                                  rend="underline"
                                                  >Stra<add>?</add>berg</hi></placeName>? and buy an
                                        estate<lb/> nott you have coming as the
                                        journa<add>?</add><lb/> take my advise and you I got
                                        your<lb/> money sue him at once. <persName>Mr<lb/>
                                                  Morrison</persName> with no justice, if the
                                        D-<lb/> finds you in earnest, he will pay at once</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">Yours</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">
                                        <persName role="author">S M Isaacs</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p><persName>M Levy</persName> from
                                                  <sic><placeName>Cincinatti</placeName></sic> is
                                        engaged<lb/> to a daughter of <persName>John M
                                                  Davis</persName><lb/> I save two
                                                  <sic>weedding</sic>
                                        <date>sunday 2</date><lb/>
                                        <add>אלה ימי הגבלה</add> and 2 in the <add>לג
                                        בעומר</add><lb/> is the order of the <add>פרו
                                        ורבו</add><lb/> day</p>
